Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.45,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.13,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.13,0:00:14.87,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.87,0:00:17.13,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あの電車に葉香ちゃん乗ってた
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.77,0:00:18.87,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.63,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんが連れていかれる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.89,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,ポンタローは何としても
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.89,0:00:41.30,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんとやらを手元に置いておきたいらしい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.30,0:00:43.26,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,7Gの鍵ってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.26,0:00:44.92,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そっか　それで
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.92,0:00:46.28,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香を連れ戻す
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.73,0:00:51.57,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香の意思で言ったのならともかく
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.89,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,無理やりだったら絶対だめ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.12,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.21,0:01:01.57,JP-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,逃がすな
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.91,JP-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,逃がすと茶碗蒸しにされるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.95,0:01:06.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,お　誠先生だ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.81,0:01:07.46,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やほー
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.46,0:01:09.21,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,ポンタローが逃げた
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.37,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,ボタンはどうした
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.37,0:01:15.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんか怪しげに隠してあったけど押しても何も起こんなかったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.18,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,駄目だ　追いかけるのなら持ってけ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.78,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,それより葉香ちゃんの方が大事ですし
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.78,0:01:21.14,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,戻るの面倒
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.79,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,前たちの目的はなんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.79,0:01:24.47,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんを取り戻す
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.47,0:01:24.99,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,それ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.99,0:01:27.16,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あと世界を元に戻す
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.81,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,それもまああるかも
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.81,0:01:31.75,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,ポンタローは本人が思うほど頭が良くない
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.24,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,行動は単純だ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.24,0:01:34.83,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,大事だったから隠した
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.83,0:01:35.42,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.21,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,そして
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.21,0:01:40.05,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,その大事なボタンを置き去りにして逃げざるを得なかった
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.91,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,いやだ　何で
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.70,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.74,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫姫
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.41,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,そんなご心配には及ばず
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.99,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,大船に乗ったつもりで
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.57,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,心配　何の
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.09,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,不埒な連中がその
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.07,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不埒
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.07,0:01:56.94,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ですです
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.94,0:01:59.49,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫の安全を脅かす者どもがおりまして
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.10,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,ですがご安心ください
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.60,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,このポンタローが誠心誠意　営業努力いたしますので
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.34,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,それでは私状況を確認してまいります
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.37,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫にはいつも通り過ごしていただかなくては
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.72,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,いつも通り
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.56,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,いつもって何だっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.68,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,寝て起きてご飯食べて勉強して
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.68,0:02:21.61,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,それから　誰か
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.03,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,今の何
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.48,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ぽち
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.48,0:02:27.99,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,きて　いないの
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.39,0:02:31.10,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,あのボタンにも意味はあるということか
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.02,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,意味
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.38,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんか特別なボタンなのかなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.35,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,単に7Gを起動する以外に
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.93,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香もボタンも両方揃ってないと駄目ってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.15,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そっかセットだ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.15,0:02:43.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.76,0:02:48.06,JP-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,そのあたりに池袋の魔女と呼ばれる理由がありそうだな
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.68,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,つまり葉香ちゃんがボタンをして
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.11,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ボタンが葉香ちゃんに力を与えて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.64,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そして世界を変えた
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.01,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,お　かしこい
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,きっとそれだね
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.08,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.38,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,ボタンを押す人間は同じ人間でなければ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.32,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,ボタンを押した中富葉香に
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.36,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,再度ボタンを押させるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.36,0:03:10.90,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,それがおそらく世界と中富葉香を元に戻す唯一の方法だ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.05,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うあ　すごい
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.57,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ　分かれてる
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　とどっち行けばいいんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　トントンと
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.08,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.53,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ええ　ボチさん分かるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,さすがポチさん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.90,0:03:53.74,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,最近妙に扱いづらいなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.74,0:03:57.46,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,このまま人形のままでいてくれないとこっちは困るんだが
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.91,0:04:09.55,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.23,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,しつこいやつらめ
