Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.11,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,邪魔
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.84,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,骨にしてやる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.31,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,邪魔
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.42,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,使えない奴らめ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.26,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あっぶなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.63,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,当たったら死んじゃうじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.40,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,馬鹿が
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.75,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,お前たちには死んでもらう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.39,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.78,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,死ぬの私たち
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.53,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.73,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,お前たちなど姫にとって一理なし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.17,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋は姫とともに
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.58,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,姫なくして池袋なし　
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.65,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋なくして姫もなう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.59,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.65,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,お前
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.47,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.81,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,こいつらをコテンパンにやってしまう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.09,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,一つ聞きたい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.73,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,池袋なくして姫もなしとはどういうことだ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.90,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,どういう意味だ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.81,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋を中心とした7Gエネルギーは
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.11,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,彼女を中心に発生している
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.07,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋と持ちつ持たれず
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.41,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,彼女が池袋を生かし　池袋が彼女を生かしている
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.53,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,えええ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.16,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,し
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.45,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香様の命を削ってか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.20,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,削って
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.07,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,どういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.86,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,人はいずれ死ぬ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.86,0:08:01.05,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋を支えるという偉業の何が不満だ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.93,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,そこに葉香様の意思はあるのか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.83,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,何か勘違いしてないか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.62,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,お前はただの用心棒だ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.26,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,私は葉香様の用心棒であって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.16,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,貴様の用心棒ではない
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.01,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,なんだと
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.46,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香様が苦しんでいるのは7Gのせいではないのか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.79,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,だったらどうした
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.68,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,7Gを止めればその苦しみはなくなるのか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.65,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.99,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,7Gが魔女王の葉香ちゃんを作り
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.22,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんが7G世界を作った
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.22,0:08:26.72,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ボタン
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.72,0:08:27.43,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.31,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ボタンを押せば
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.87,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,このけらつ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.54,0:08:38.69,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.46,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香様は頼む
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.02,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,敵じゃないってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.89,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香のことに関しては仲間
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.46,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,って考えていい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.13,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.14,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香様
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.14,0:09:04.94,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ぽち
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.26,JP-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,茶をどうぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.51,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.07,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大丈夫かな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.92,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,多分
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.67,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,きっと葉香ちゃんだって分かってくれるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.33,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,分かってくれなかったら
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.70,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,この練りありぽんを見せたらきっと
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.47,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,渋たぞをちょっと読めばもしかしたら
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.20,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃんそれ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.71,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あ　銀梅花
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.65,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんと関係なくない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.50,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.43,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんでだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.59,0:09:41.68,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.19,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんが星みたいだねって言ったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.30,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.06,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いつ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.45,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ずっと前　学校菜園で
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.44,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,へえ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃんその頃からずっと星のこと考えてたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.46,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香分かる
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.03,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私だよ　静留
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.15,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.33,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,忘れちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,思い出せない
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あのさ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.30,0:10:06.37,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんか　許してほしいわけじゃないんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.66,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最悪
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.14,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最悪っていうか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.69,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,許してくれなくてもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.40,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ただ葉香を傷つけたことだけは謝りたくて
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.83,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんて基本的に口下手だから
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.56,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,共感性羞恥
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.37,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,本当の気持ちじゃなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.64,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘘　ちょっとは本当だった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.88,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あのね私馬鹿じゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.49,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,馬鹿だから葉香がすごく偉く見えて
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.49,0:10:33.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香が偉い分　自分がどんどん駄目になって気がして
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.80,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,だから　わざと嫌な言い方した
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.33,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でも　それも
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.72,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それがダメダメだったってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.28,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,今はわかる
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.64,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.97,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,全然平気
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.80,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香が怒るの当たり前だも
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.03,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.84,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん止めて
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.73,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ね　何で葉香ちゃんが静留ちゃんを攻撃するの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.64,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん分かっないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.99,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,嫌だ　何
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.39,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,思い　思い出したの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.71,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ていうか無理だよね　葉香には
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.70,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,あまり大きなこと言うと恥ずかしいっていうか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.37,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,知らないから　ねもう葉香のことなんか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.72,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょ　やめないよ葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.53,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怖いよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.51,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,として
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.85,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,言ったこと
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,言った
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.00,0:11:44.06,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,言ったたけど　葉香に離れていってほしくなかったから
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.47,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,今　今ならわかる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.78,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,わかるよ　わかってる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.88,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どうせ無理無理ダメダメっていうのがどれだけひどいことか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.88,0:11:52.78,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でもその時は
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香を傷つけても許りしても言ってほしくなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.39,0:12:00.18,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,そのせいで吾野を飛び出した私を連れ戻しに来たの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.15,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.50,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私が言ったことを謝りたかった
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.03,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,後　葉香のやりたいことを信じるし
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.37,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,支えたいし　応援したいって言いたかった
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.94,0:12:12.49,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,自分の主張ばかりですごい傲慢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.11,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.11,0:12:13.90,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.90,0:12:14.81,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,言い過ぎ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.59,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香ちゃん　それは違うよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.21,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんは確かにひどいことを言ったと思う
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.92,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,でもただの傲慢だったら
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.11,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,2年間毎日探したりしないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.87,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋まで来ないし
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.84,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そうだよ　大変だったんだから
