Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.69,0:21:10.35,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,戻ってきたんだね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.62,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あたしたちも戻ってきた
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,戻ってきたのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.49,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,新しい未知の新宿線だったり
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.79,0:21:21.27,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あたしたちが別の世界線に飛んだ可能性もあるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちゃんと吾野に帰れるかな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.27,0:21:23.96,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,それ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.33,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,ね　静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.02,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,なんで「アポジー号」って名前つけたの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.02,0:21:28.66,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.45,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.45,0:21:35.09,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そういえば静留ちゃんにしては珍しいよね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.09,0:21:36.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,専門用語だし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.05,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何で
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.26,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何で何で
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.15,0:21:48.71,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地球と月が　一番離れたところがアボジーで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.82,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あとは近づくだけだから
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.98,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:14.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:17.13,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香坐上了那輛列車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:18.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.63,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香被人帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.89,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,龐太郎無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:41.30,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,都不得不把葉香留在自己身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:43.26,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,難道說她是7G的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:44.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,對啊 很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:46.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們把葉香給帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:51.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,先不說是不是葉香本人的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果是被迫的話絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.12,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:01.57,ZH-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,不准逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.91,ZH-Main-Down,Leader,0,0,0,,你們跑了我們會被變成蛋羹的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:06.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 誠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:07.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,呀吼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:09.21,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,龐太郎逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.37,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,按鈕怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:15.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,雖然藏起來就挺可疑的 但按下去什麼也沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.18,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不行 你們要追就必須帶上按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說起來葉香的事情才更為重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:21.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,回去很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.79,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你們的目的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:24.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,奪回葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:24.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就這
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:27.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,還有把世界恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這個好像也有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:31.75,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,龐太郎本人並沒有他想像中的那麼聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.24,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,行動很純粹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:34.83,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,因為很重要所以才會有所隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:35.42,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.21,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:40.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,他不得不拋棄那個重要的按鈕而逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.91,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不要 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.70,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.74,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.41,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您無需這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.99,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我們已經乘上了「大船」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.57,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,擔心 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.09,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那些不講道理的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.07,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不講道理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:56.94,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:59.49,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,他們那群人是會威脅到公主的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.10,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,所以請您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.60,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我龐太郎會一心一意 努力工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.34,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那麼我現在就去確認一下狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.37,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主像往常一樣生活就可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.72,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,往常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.56,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,往常是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.68,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,睡覺 起床 吃飯 學習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:21.61,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,然後是 誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.03,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,剛剛那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,博奇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:27.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,快來 你不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:31.10,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,所以說那個按鈕也有什麼意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,會是什麼特別的按鈕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,除了啟動7G以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香和按鈕兩者缺一不可 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,對啊 組合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:43.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:48.06,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,或許這就是她被稱為池袋魔女的緣由了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是說葉香按下了按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,按鈕給予了葉香力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.64,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,然後世界就被改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,肯定就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.08,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.38,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,如果「解鈴不是繫鈴人」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.32,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,開啟按鈕的中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.36,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,需要她再按一次關閉按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:10.90,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,這恐怕是讓世界和中富葉香恢復如初的唯一辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.05,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 道路分叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 走 走哪條路為好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 哪條哪條
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 波奇它知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不愧是波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:53.74,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,最近的都好難對付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你要是不好好當個人偶我可就犯難了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:09.55,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.23,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,糾纏不休的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.58,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是我 你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.53,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,給老子快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 前方危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.25,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行 這距離根本聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.35,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.07,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,難道我會坐以待斃把公主拱手讓出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.03,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:57.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們去到對面的車上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:05:59.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但但但但是但是要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:02.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:04.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.14,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.75,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:15.50,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果萬一回到之前 肯定要追究7G的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.15,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這種事情絕對不能發生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啊 終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.62,ZH-Main-Down,Chaos,0,0,0,,毀滅我的國家可是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.76,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我會馬上改變你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,別搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.84,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,把你做成骨辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.42,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,中了的話就會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.40,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.75,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你們這群人都得去死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要死的是我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.53,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.73,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你們對於公主來說毫無存在的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.17,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋和公主是同一的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.58,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,沒有公主就沒有池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.65,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,所以沒有池袋也就沒有公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.59,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.65,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,把這群傢伙全部都揍扁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.09,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我就問一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.73,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,沒有池袋也就沒有公主 是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.90,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,以池袋為中心所放射的7G能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.11,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是以她為中心所產生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.07,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,不論是否擁有池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.41,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她與池袋都是「同生」的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.45,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,這會削減葉香大人的壽命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,削減
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.07,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.86,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,人終究要死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:01.05,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,而她的死支撐起了池袋這一偉業 有何不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.93,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,那這是葉香大人的意願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.83,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你是不是搞錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.62,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你不過只是個保鏢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.26,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我是葉香大人的保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.16,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,不是你這傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人的痛苦難道不是因為7G造成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是那又能怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.68,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,如果7G停止的話痛苦是否就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,7G讓葉香成為了魔女大王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香也能夠「創造」7G的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:26.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:27.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只要按下按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.87,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:38.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你不是我們的敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只要是關心葉香的都是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這樣認為可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.13,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.14,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:04.94,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,博奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.26,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,請喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.07,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,多半問題不大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.67,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香肯定會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是她不明白的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這本練愛給她看後肯定就能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,給她讀點澀澤的書說不定也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子姐那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這和葉香不無關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.43,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:41.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香說過自己想像星星一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.30,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,很久之前 在學校花園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香從那時候開始就一直在想著星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香你想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是我啊 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.15,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你忘了我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是記不起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:06.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個 我不是來懇求你的原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,說起來最壞的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不原諒我也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只是 我想為我傷害到葉香的行為而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留實際上算是不善言辭的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,羞恥感同身受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那本不是我真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 雖然有點是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個不是說 我是個笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因為我是個笨蛋 所以葉香看起來非常偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:33.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但葉香這麼厲害 自己卻妄自菲薄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以 我才會說出難聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 這也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這些也是「不可為之」的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,現在的我才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香生氣是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.03,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.84,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.73,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吶 為什麼葉香要攻擊靜留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香你這樣我們不理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,討厭 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想 想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.71,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,「再說了葉香你 不行的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.70,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,「牛皮吹太大了也會不好意思的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.37,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,「我根本對葉香你 一無所知啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會 別這樣啊葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.85,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,會說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:44.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然這些是我說的 但我也不希望葉香離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,現在 現在的我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白 我真的明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「否定他人」總之是一件很過分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:52.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不論是否已經傷害到了葉香 這些都如鯁在喉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:12:00.18,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,所以你是因為這樣才從吾野出來 準備把我接回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.15,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想為我所說過的話而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,之後 我願意相信葉香的所行之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想告訴你 我願意支持你 為你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:12.49,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,自顧自的主張 如此傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:13.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:14.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,話太超過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香 這肯定不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我認為葉香她確實說了些很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但如果這只是傲慢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她根本不會在兩年間每天都去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也根本不會來池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是啊 真的非常辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.66,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我沒有拜託她 所以毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊 沒有拜託我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.61,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是若你還是這樣拒絕 葉香也只能「這樣下去」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:34.84,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:38.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我以前一直認為這樣下去就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:42.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一直都在吾野 和葉香還有大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以最初我就想找回葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 現在的我才明白這是多麼「無趣」的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:51.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很無聊啊 一開始就知道結果是什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:54.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,探索未知未解的事物 會越來越有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:59.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,聽我說 我們從吾野來到池袋這 經歷了九九八十一難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是都非常的有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這些全部 都是待在吾野所不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:06.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但就是說 現在的世界是不會變化的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.25,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是「固定的狀態」對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,真的非常悲慘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.86,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而且世界好像還在縮小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我希望改變 想要改變自我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香實際上也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.87,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,別一廂情願說自己是「真心」的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.04,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,現在你快樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.17,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,並不 快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,並不快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野發生了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,無論悲傷 還是痛苦 抑或艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 這些都很「快樂」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.46,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香 你有一個夢想對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但現在這樣什麼也不會被改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只有把世界恢復如初 才有可能實現夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.61,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只要努力就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.15,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,必然有這種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.86,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再次讓世界「運作」起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.81,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.37,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,做不到的話會很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,實現不了夢想很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:56.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是我 會永遠支持葉香的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:59.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為你兩肋插刀 在所不辭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:04.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「不做而後悔」和「做了而後悔」大相徑庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以我會支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那是天狼星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,天狼星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.03,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,承諾之星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:23.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個 向著那顆亮晶晶的承諾之星約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.47,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,承諾之星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剛剛給它取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.61,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,它的名字應該是叫「天狼星」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那麼 就把它作為我們「承諾」的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.61,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.54,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我根本沒有資格成為你所支持之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.82,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我一直把靜留你當成傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.35,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,話說得很有勇氣 卻什麼也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,明明根本做不成什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:56.08,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,你要一直這樣下去 腐朽愚笨下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.05,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,或被嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.22,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,或被詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想這不是什麼「詛咒」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是「祈願」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,畢竟我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然我一直都待在吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但無論你去到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:13.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我都很高興 你能放下這些「為我的考慮」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:18.00,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,笨蛋 靜留你真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,聽說我 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:23.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比起一個人在這 和大家一起更好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.28,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那樣的話絕對會很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:29.14,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今後的事情 交給今後彼時彼刻的自己考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.44,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.53,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,別想按下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:08.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.51,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,哈 嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.13,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.42,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這可大吃一驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.88,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不是魔女公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是葉香 中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.76,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.31,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,如果世界恢復如初
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.58,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,即便世界無法復原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那時候再考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,樂觀主義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這 不也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.72,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.17,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡是 哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:30.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是這樣的 還是不是這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香是這樣的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.40,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.60,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 和我認知中的葉香匹配度百分百
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.40,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,感覺和以前有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.40,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.84,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,就算河流從同一區域流過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:50.38,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,所經行的水也不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.87,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,城市 人們 世界也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.72,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,看似相同 實則不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:55.99,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,一切都在「變化」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:59.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,又說了這麼帥氣哲學的總結台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.40,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界也不會完全恢復如初
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.89,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,變化才是永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:03.45,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.49,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我要去「確認」這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.66,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,有緣再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.30,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:20.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感謝與讚美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,非此即彼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.31,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,可是大家都變回了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.63,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是變回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:29.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而是原來由人類變成僵屍的人們 再度變成人類而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.43,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我還是你們的女王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 這確實很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.82,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,黑木女王 很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.37,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你們要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.33,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,出發確認
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:53.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,「遠地點號」出發前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.44,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,遠地點號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是靜留起的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:09.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野 現在怎樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,難道會不知道怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.01,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,終於聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.67,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,果然還是因為7G停止了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:28.17,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.14,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.41,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,雖然高興和不高興的都有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.09,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不如說難以判斷的事情同時發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.74,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,全部的影響不能說都消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:39.84,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,一些 不對 剩下的問題還很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:40.72,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,把所有人的變化都記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:42.97,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,真是真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.33,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,誠大老師可真是用人不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.68,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.53,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,今天的哈吧吧模式比起昨天延長了39秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:53.92,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,嘛就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.44,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,回家路上要注意好安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.91,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,說不定 這條道路也不會一帆風順啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:03.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,有什麼東西在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.56,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,其它的線路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,難不成是西武新宿線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:10.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,竟然回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們也回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那可是新的未知的新宿線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:21.27,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我們進入到其它的世界線也是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,到底能不能回到吾野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:23.96,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.33,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,吶 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.02,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,為什麼你要起「遠地點號」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:28.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:35.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說起來靜留這樣還挺少見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:36.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,畢竟是專業術語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:48.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地球與月亮 相隔最遠的地方就是「遠地點」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那麼之後 便是「靠近」了
